title: Bobby’s Dog Has His First Medial Issue  +  Grace Potter and Walker Burroughs from American Idol stop by + Bobby Tests Out New Joke Material

description:
Bobby first medical issue with his new pup has popped up. It's called a dog "cheery eye" and he will be going to the vet today to find out more. Grace Potter and Walker Burroughs stop by and Bobby tests out some joke options for AMC Honors tonight.
